OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain will
OL,6,Fspread from the west this evening.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will see
OL,8,Fspells of rain, becoming persistent
OL,9,Fand occasionally heavy later. Fresh to
OL,10,Fstrong southwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FRain, heavy at times, will
OL,13,Fclear from the west in the morning.
OL,14,FThen becoming brighter with showers.
OL,15,FFresh southwesterly winds. Cold.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCold
OL,18,Fwith bright spells and showers on
OL,19,FFriday and Saturday. Rain spreading
OL,20,Feast on Sunday followed by a few
OL,21,Fshowers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
